{
  "texts": [
    "Indexed libraries were pooled in an equimolar fashion and sequenced on a NovaSeq 6000 instrument in a PE28/120 run using the NovaSeq 6000 SP Reagent Kit (200 cycles) (Illumina).",
    "An average of 228 million paired reads were generated per sample.",
    "Tissues were stained with H&E, and slides were scanned on a Pannoramic MIDI scanner (3DHISTECH) using a ×20, 0.8-NA objective.",
    "Quality metrics for the collected ST data are shown in Supplementary Table 5.",
    "CODEX data collection and preprocessing."
  ]
}